verbose_text: We ultimately had two primary goals for examining changes in HbA 1c and BGMF : First, we were interested in the prediction of the HbA 1c slope from the BGMF slope where we examined a statistical model with the HbA 1c slope as the outcome variable, the BGMF slope was the primary predictor, and we also controlled for the initial levels of HbA 1c and BGMF from their respective trajectories (i.e., the intercepts) and the set of covariates detailed in the previous section.
